Package org.eclipse.imagen.media.jiffle.parser

Class ExpressionWorker

Object
JiffleBaseListener
BaseWorker
PropertyWorker<JiffleType>
ExpressionWorker
All Implemented Interfaces:
ParseTreeListener, JiffleListener
public class ExpressionWorker extends PropertyWorker<JiffleType>
Labels expression nodes with their Jiffle types. Expects that the parse tree has been previously annotated by a VarWorker.
Author:
michael
